Source: I004 and `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-17-visible-quota-configuration.md`, Task 3.

Migrate `configGeneral.qml` provider groups, checkboxes, provider/global resets, and advanced JSON projection to `VisibleQuotaConfig.configuration()`. Write cfg only for returned `changed:true` event results and delete the local catalogue, hydration, edit, default-comparison, and serialisation choreography.

Acceptance: KCM source contracts prove all visible-quota UI state crosses the module; opening/projecting configuration performs no write; checkbox/reset effects persist only returned compatible JSON; advanced raw text remains supported; no migrated visibility policy remains in QML; configuration, visibility, and layout regressions pass.
